title: Flight Simulator 2020 - Sightseeing - F1 Sepang racing track
description:
In this video we will fly over the the F1 Sepang racing track which has been used for the F1 races in Malaysia. Before the cars go on the track we will fly over the circuit using a Airbus H135 helicopter with Red Bull Livery.
